{"id":"meshillemoth","term":"Meshillemoth","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Requitals. (1.) The father of Berechiah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 28:12\">2 Chr. 28:12</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) A priest, the son of Immer (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 11:13\">Neh. 11:13</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Chronicles 28:12","Nehemiah 11:13"]}